textbackslash}backslash\$r\${\textbackslash}backslash\$noccurring, based on a coupled reaction involving Mn oxides (or possibly highly labile Fe oxides)\${\textbackslash}backslash\$r\${\textbackslash}backslash\$nburied during small-scale slumping events. However, to fully investigate this coupling, advances in\${\textbackslash}backslash\$r\${\textbackslash}backslash\$nthe capability of high-resolution pore-water techniques are required.},
